# NOTE: package-lock.json is deliberately NOT ignored. The Pages workflow runs
# `npm ci`, which requires the lockfile to be committed.

# No raw media in git. The legacy site tracked an 83MB MP4 and autoplayed it.
# Commit compressed web derivatives only. See docs/playables.md §Media weight.
*.mov
Media/**/*.mp4
